 based on real project structures used with clients like Cuculus, JetShop, and Origo.\"}],[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"flex flex-col gap-[120px] max-md:gap-[60px]\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"div\",\"Deliverable 1\",{\"className\":\"grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-16 max-md:gap-10 items-center\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"font-mono text-[13px] uppercase tracking-[0.65px] text-[#0a1926]/40 mb-4\",\"children\":\"Deliverable 1\"}],[\"$\",\"h3\",null,{\"className\":\"text-[clamp(24px,3vw,40px)] leading-[1.15] font-normal text-[#0a1926] mb-6\",\"children\":\"Legacy system assessment\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"text-[#333333] text-[18px] leading-[1.6]\",\"children\":\"A comprehensive architecture analysis of the current system — dependency mapping, tech debt quantification, and identification of the components that block roadmap delivery. This gives you a clear picture of where modernization effort should focus first.\"}]]}],[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"\",\"children\":[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"bg-[#f5f5f5] rounded-xl aspect-[4/3] flex items-center justify-center text-[#0a1926]/30 text-[18px] font-mono\",\"children\":\"Legacy System Assessment\"}]}]]}],[\"$\",\"div\",\"Deliverable 2\",{\"className\":\"grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-16 max-md:gap-10 items-center\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"md:order-2\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"font-mono text-[13px] uppercase tracking-[0.65px] text-[#0a1926]/40 mb-4\",\"children\":\"Deliverable 2\"}],[\"$\",\"h3\",null,{\"className\":\"text-[clamp(24px,3vw,40px)] leading-[1.15] font-normal text-[#0a1926] mb-6\",\"children\":\"Migration feasibility report\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"text-[#333333] text-[18px] leading-[1.6]\",\"children\":\"Stack evaluation, risk analysis, and upgrade path validation for the recommended migration strategy. Includes a comparison of approaches (phased vs. big